title: Travelogue 360 Paris
description: Among its renowned landmarks and hidden gems waiting to be discovered, Paris holds something new for each of its visitors. Scour some of the world&#039;s most famous locations for souvenirs as you prepare to be interviewed for an upcoming article in Travelogue 360 magazine! Locate items hidden in 3-Dimensional views of the Eiffel Tower, down the Champs Elysees, under the Arc d&#039;Triomphe, and other Parisian landmarks! There are 22 eye-catching locales in all as well as fun facts and mini-games galore!
